Rug (nest, bed) for a pet
For those who want to send pdf with photos in the direct (just write in the comments) (translation compiled with the help of Google translator)

1. 6 sc in Adjustable Ring
2. sc inc every st - 12
3. sc inc every 2nd - 18
4. sc inc every 3rd - 24
5. sc inc every 4th - 30
6. sc inc every 5th - 36
7. sc inc every 6th - 42
8. sc inc every 7th ‚Äì 48
9. sc inc every 8th ‚Äì 54
10. sc inc every 9th ‚Äì 60

Next, knit the side so that it is perpendicular to the bottom of our rug:

11. 60 sc ‚Äì 60
12.¬†sc dec every 9th ‚Äì 54
13-15. 54 sc ‚Äì 54
16. sc dec every 7th ‚Äì 48

Wrap side up and sew between 3 and 4 rows of rug (from the edge), at the same time we fill our side with filler.
